President Dr Arif Alvi and Begum Samina Alvi Saturday wished quick recovery to President of Turkey Recep Tayyab Erdogan and his wife Emine Erdogan from COVID.
In a tweet on social media platform Twitter, he said, “I and Mrs @Saminalvi  wish Mr Tayyab  @RTErdogan  & Mrs Emine Erdogan quick recovery from Covid. واذا مرضت فھو یشفین We pray to Allah to give them health & long life. These wishes and prayers are also from all Pakistanis.”
